{"tid":827060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左 大節日都係想同屋企人過","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T06:38:14.000Z","uid":194435,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f13e4ca1ddc3035b0f29278d22a7273507bf8059","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"黎緊就中秋節 有感而發 <br />\n可能有啲長 不過好想分享<br />\n<br />\n先講講我屋企習慣 <br />\n每逢大節日<br />\n大約20幾個親戚都會聚埋搞bbq過節<br />\n但我由小五開始到前年大一都無參加過<br />\n<br />\n記得以前小學同初中<br />\n已經有一個好想出去玩既心<br />\n覺得成班人出去玩好開心<br />\n只要見到班朋友 坐成晚公園都覺得好正<br />\n有一種講唔出既滿足感<br />\n仲可能覺得自己可以出去玩好威<br />\n<br />\n去到高中<br />\n已經變到出去同朋友過節日<br />\n係一件好理所當然既事<br />\n什至仲會笑身邊朋友要陪屋企人<br />\n或者屋企人唔比節日出街<br />\n出到去成班男女一定要嘈<br />\n成晚不停吹水 咩遊戲都會玩一餐<br />\n總之係一班人過通宵就得<br />\n<br />\n但去到上年大二既時候<br />\n突然唔想出去玩 好想同屋企人過<br />\n朋友問係咪照舊出去通宵<br />\n我就話 唔啦我想同屋企bbq<br />\n<br />\n可能因為人大左 好多野都自己話事<br />\n幾時出街都得 出到幾夜又得好<br />\n覺得如果節日又係見平時既朋友<br />\n反而無同屋企人一齊過咁有氣氛<br />\n老實講 我屋企會搞bbq呢個習慣<br />\n其實好幸福 節日一年先一次<br />\n都唔知仲可以有幾多次呢啲屋企聚會<br />\n<br />\n我既意思唔係叫你大節日先陪屋企人<br />\n當然平日都要陪多啲<br />\n只不過同屋企人過既氣氛 可能不停倒數緊<br />\n嗰份溫暖你係朋友身上搵唔到<br />\n所以好好珍惜屋企人<br />\n<br />\n最後 提早祝大家有個開心既中秋節<br />\n同屋企人定朋友過都好<br />\n總之人月兩團圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4341cd5297389f7f6fd6c0ef8f2857fd3215c39d","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋節同屋企人bbq真係好開心"},{"pid":"50de4f73e8b49637e1662689ff86c8200bedd5db","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"我係想強調 同朋友幾時都有<br />\n但節日一年一次<br />\n當然同屋企人過氣氛更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e181c5ecd3b1cda90ed3d11fdae28b94b9e64cfe","tid":827060,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5160cf449a02acd7eda9d920256b3e71a447c209","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4341cd5297389f7f6fd6c0ef8f2857fd3215c39d","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋節同屋企人bbq真係好開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"係 成班20幾人<br />\n一齊bbq 賞月飲下酒 又食月餅<br />\n雖然未必會通宵<br />\n但嗰幾個鐘真係好珍惜"},{"pid":"7181ca03f60d54924ec5f80fb3047feb1f0efb94","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e181c5ecd3b1cda90ed3d11fdae28b94b9e64cfe","tid":827060,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"你中秋節會點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d214665fca17c3afa547036b37a1c66e0aeefb","tid":827060,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"本來以前聖誕節好恨同朋友出去過，覺得好似變大人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從有一次睇咗集我們這一家，嗰集講花師奶見到佢兩個仔女開始出去同朋友過節，覺得好感慨子女終有一日會離開家庭，剩番花師奶同花老爺兩個，覺得有啲寂莫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知我啊媽有無咁諗，但我睇完突然覺得佢可能每逢過節都無我都會有啲寂莫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0c4b5e549559d25f78b44b6fcee081bd251eac","tid":827060,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fc359da366dc21fc71f31025d72badcc2fd207f","tid":827060,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"但多數提前食飯<br />\n正日都係留係屋企<br />\n屋企人仲問我點解唔出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bfdd7e2bf2ee340d946e13cea496e65ceb89bd","tid":827060,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7181ca03f60d54924ec5f80fb3047feb1f0efb94","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e181c5ecd3b1cda90ed3d11fdae28b94b9e64cfe","tid":827060,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"你中秋節會點過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"Fd 子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293f6bae4af97d80dcad70403cc214fee4054757","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73d214665fca17c3afa547036b37a1c66e0aeefb","tid":827060,"uid":77959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"本來以前聖誕節好恨同朋友出去過，覺得好似變大人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從有一次睇咗集我們這一家，嗰集講花師奶見到佢兩個仔女開始出去同朋友過節，覺得好感慨子女終有一日會離開家庭，剩番花師奶同花老爺兩個，覺得有啲寂莫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知我啊媽有無咁諗，但我睇完突然覺得佢可能每逢過節都無我都會有啲寂莫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"我都成日睇我們這一家<br />\n你比佢影響到 所以要更識諗<br />\n講真 屋企人唔會介意你出去玩<br />\n但心入面 當然想你都係身邊一齊過"},{"pid":"23a1ea9499124fc5522f7e23da6ba231fec66893","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f0c4b5e549559d25f78b44b6fcee081bd251eac","tid":827060,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實每年一次家庭聚會<br />\n都係每年倒數緊<br />\n所以平日都要多啲陪屋企人"},{"pid":"2d79f79257a069fa7221725ec33cceac9ed50c9c","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"大家可以講下自己點過大節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e9b0f062e9f175aba3520894ab7e50aeb82941","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5160cf449a02acd7eda9d920256b3e71a447c209","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4341cd5297389f7f6fd6c0ef8f2857fd3215c39d","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋節同屋企人bbq真係好開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"係 成班20幾人<br />\n一齊bbq 賞月飲下酒 又食月餅<br />\n雖然未必會通宵<br />\n但嗰幾個鐘真係好珍惜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"好warm"},{"pid":"66a080987a955a5b013b1d7c90993d78710e6765","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32e9b0f062e9f175aba3520894ab7e50aeb82941","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5160cf449a02acd7eda9d920256b3e71a447c209","tid":827060,"uid":194435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4341cd5297389f7f6fd6c0ef8f2857fd3215c39d","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋節同屋企人bbq真係好開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"係 成班20幾人<br />\n一齊bbq 賞月飲下酒 又食月餅<br />\n雖然未必會通宵<br />\n但嗰幾個鐘真係好珍惜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"好warm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你呢係咪都係同屋企人過？"},{"pid":"f8aace8d182f9572da48ed5f4a4da10a4d534363","tid":827060,"uid":201309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p